OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FJoe Thompson's wife Chantelle and 12-
OL,7,Fyear-old daughter Lula talk to ITV
OL,8,FGranada's Sports Correspondent Mike
OL,9,FHall.
OL,11,FThe daughter of footballer Joe
OL,12,FThompson, who died last month aged
OL,13,Fjust 36, has said he was the 'best
OL,14,Fdad' who just 'loved to help people'.
OL,16,FLula Thompson 12, described the
OL,17,FRochdale star as 'funny' and
OL,18,F'positive' and said she had 'so many
OL,19,Fspecial memories' of their time
OL,20,Ftogether.
