OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FJoe died in April after being
OL,7,Fdiagnosed three times with cancer.
OL,9,FJoe was a legend at his former club
OL,10,FRochdale and respected across the
OL,11,Fsporting community for the way in
OL,12,Fwhich he faced adversity and for his
OL,13,Ffundraising.
OL,15,FHis family have issued an open
OL,16,Finvitation to his supporters to attend
OL,17,Fhis funeral on May 12, saying it was
OL,18,FJoe's wishes to have a big crowd there
OL,19,Fto say goodbye.
