OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FHis wife Chantelle described Joe as
OL,7,F"an incredible man" whose "heart was
OL,8,Fhumongous".
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV Granada's sports
OL,11,Fcorrespondent Mike Hall, she said Joe
OL,12,Fwas "thoughtful and passionate", an
OL,13,Famazing dad, husband and brother, and
OL,14,Fsomeone who "lit up the room".
OL,16,FShe said he was "full of positivity,
OL,17,Feven until the very last day".
