OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FChantelle added: "People say we've had
OL,7,Fsome tough times, which we have - with
OL,8,Fthe three cancer diagnoses, we lost
OL,9,Fbaby Dre in 2021 but even throughout
OL,10,Fthose times we've managed to make the
OL,11,Fbest of the situations and we've made
OL,12,Fsome incredible memories.
OL,14,F"And I think we wouldn't maybe have
OL,15,Fbeen as focussed on spending time
OL,16,Ftogether and creating those memories
OL,17,Fif it wasn't for the diagnoses at the
OL,18,Fstart because that kind of made us
OL,19,Frealise life is too short to not be
OL,20,Fdoing that."
