OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FJoe was first diagnosed with Hodgkin
OL,7,Flymphoma in 2013 and recovered before
OL,8,Fthe cancer returned in 2017. He went
OL,9,Fon to recover a second time.
OL,11,FJoe revealed in March last year that
OL,12,Fhe had stage four lymphoma which had
OL,13,Fspread to his lungs. He died in April
OL,14,Fwith his family beside him.
OL,16,FHis career started at Manchester
OL,17,FUnited and ended in Rochdale where in
OL,18,F2018, he scored the goal which kept
OL,19,Fthe club in the Football League,
OL,20,Fearning him legendary status.
