OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,FLula said she still believes her dad
OL,7,Fis with her.
OL,9,FShe recounted how she'd been on a walk
OL,10,Fjust a week after her dad had passed
OL,11,Faway and after asking for a sign, had
OL,12,Flooked down to find a row of feathers
OL,13,Fon the ground..
OL,15,FLula talks about the signs she
OL,16,Fbelieves her dad sent her:
OL,18,FJoe's funeral will take place on
OL,19,FMonday 12 May at St Mark's Church in
OL,20,FWorsley. His family have issued an
OL,21,Fopen invitation for anyone to attend.
