OL,3,CDaughter's moving tribute to
OL,4,Cfootballer dad Joe Thompson
OL,6,F"It was Joe's wishes," Chantelle said.
OL,8,F"We spoke about this prior to him
OL,9,Fpassing. He said he wanted anyone who
OL,10,Ffelt he had impacted them in any way
OL,11,Fwhether by football, personally or
OL,12,Fwork.
OL,14,F"He didn't want it to be a closed
OL,15,Ffuneral. A little bit of his ego would
OL,16,Flove to see a lot of people there."
